{"ts": "2026-06-09T16:33:28.979585+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's a summary of the setup and day-to-day development commands for this repository:\n\n## Package Manager\nThis project uses **pnpm** (v10.20.0, enforced via `preinstall` script).\n\n## Prerequisites\n- **Node.js**: v24 (specified in `.nvmrc`)\n\n## Setup / Install\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n## Development Commands\n\n| Purpose | Command | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| **Dev server** (hot-reload) | `pnpm run dev` | Starts Vite dev server |\n| **Build** (production) | `pnpm run build` | Vite production build |\n| **Preview** (production build) | `pnpm run preview` | Preview the production build locally |\n| **Build & Preview** | `pnpm run build-preview` | Combines build + preview in one command |\n| **Unit tests** | `pnpm run test:unit` | Runs Vitest in watch mode |\n| **Unit tests (with coverage)** | `pnpm run test:unit-coverage` | Runs Vitest once with coverage report |\n| **Lint** | `pnpm run lint` | ESLint check on `**/*.{vue,ts,js}` files |\n| **Lint & fix** | `pnpm run lint-fix` | ESLint auto-fix on `**/*.{vue,ts,js}` files |\n\n## Additional Tooling\n- **Husky** git hooks are set up via `pnpm run prepare` (runs automatically after install).\n- **lint-staged** is configured for pre-commit checks.\n- **commitlint** enforces conventional commit messages.\n- **Prettier** is available for code formatting (`prettier.config.js` is present).", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 394, "prompt_tokens": 10543, "total_tokens": 10937, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 18, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 10304}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "e2eb81952003447e805b33007cace713", "finish_reason": 